          Experience the perfect blend of luxury, wellness, and tradition in the heart of Pahalgam. Your sanctuary for relaxation, fitness, and rejuvenation.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Social Media -->
        <div class="flex gap-3 pt-2">
          <a 
            href="#" 
            aria-label="Facebook" 
            class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-vintage-gold/10 hover:bg-vintage-gold text-vintage-gold hover:text-white rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110"
          >
            <ReactIcon name="FaFacebookF" size={18} />
          </a>
          <a 
            href="#" 
            aria-label="Instagram" 
            class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-vintage-gold/10 hover:bg-vintage-gold text-vintage-gold hover:text-white rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110"
